#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Learning touch typing with &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "Klaviatuuril kirjutama õppimine &i18n-ktouch;i abil"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &i18n-ktouch;?"
msgstr "Mis on &i18n-ktouch;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning to touch type."
msgstr "&i18n-ktouch; on klaviatuuril kirjutama õppimise rakendus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; provides you with text to train on and adjusts to different "
"levels depending on how good you are. It shows your keyboard and indicates "
"which key to press next and the correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; pakub välja teksti, mille kirjutamist saad harjutada, ning "
"võimaldab seda teha sõltuvalt sinu oskustest päris mitmel tasemel. Rakendus "
"võib näidata, millist klahvi järgmisena vajutada, ja ühtlasi osutada, "
"millise sõrmega oleks seda õige teha."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch;i peaaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch;i peaaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a touch typing tutor aimed mostly at personal use. You "
"learn typing with all fingers, step by step, without having to look down at "
"the keyboard all the time to find the right keys which slows you down a lot."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; on eelkõige isiklikuks kasutamiseks mõeldud klaviatuuril "
"kirjutama õppimise rakendus. See õpetab samm-sammult edasi liikudes "
"kirjutama kõigi sõrmedega, ilma et peaksid kogu aeg klaviatuurile vaatama "
"(mis aeglustab tugevasti kirjutamiskiirust)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Omadused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In its current version, &i18n-ktouch; has quite a number of features, such "
"as:"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch;i praegune versioon pakub mitmeid kasulikke omadusi, sealhulgas:"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ships with dozens different courses in many languages and a comfortable "
"course editor"
msgstr ""
"Paljude erinevate harjutuste pakkumine paljudes keeltes ja käepärane "
"õppetundide redaktor"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Support for different keyboard layouts with the ability to use and edit user-"
"defined layouts"
msgstr ""
"Paljude klaviatuuripaigutuste ning kasutaja enda määratud paigutuse "
"kasutamise toetus"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During your training session &i18n-ktouch; collects comprehensive "
"statistical information to help you or your teacher analyze your progress"
msgstr ""
"Põhjaliku statistilise teabe kogumine harjutamise ajal, mis aitab hiljem sul "
"endal või õpetajal sinu edusamme analüüsida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many more features which will be discussed in the appropriate "
"chapters of this manual."
msgstr ""
"Omadusi on mõistagi arvukalt rohkem ning neist tehakse edaspidi käsiraamatus "
"sobivates kohtades pikemalt juttu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting started"
msgstr "Alustamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here's another screenshot of &i18n-ktouch; in action, this time with a "
"German keyboard and training lesson:"
msgstr ""
"Siin on veel üks &i18n-ktouch;i pilt, sedakorda saksa klaviatuuripaigutuse "
"ja saksakeelse harjutusega:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch;i peaaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch;i peaaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even though learning touch typing with &i18n-ktouch; and using the program "
"should be very simple we will look a bit closer at &i18n-ktouch; in the "
"following sections."
msgstr ""
"Kuigi klaviatuuril kirjutama õppimine &i18n-ktouch;i abil ning üldse "
"rakenduse kasutamine on imelihtne, tutvustame siiski &i18n-ktouch;i lähemalt "
"järgmistes osades."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating your first profile"
msgstr "Oma esimese profiili loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time you start &i18n-ktouch; it will open a special screen helping "
"you to create your first profile. You can choose the name of your profile "
"and the level of your typing skills."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch;i esimesel käivitamisel ilmub eriline ekraan, mis aitab luua "
"sinu esimese profiili. Selles saab valida enda nime ja senise "
"kirjutamisoskuse taseme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The level you choose determines the general operation of &i18n-ktouch;. In "
"beginner mode lessons are unlocked one by one after you pass them, for "
"advanced typist all lessons are available right from the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Valitud tase määrab kindlaks &i18n-ktouch;i üldise toimimisviisi. Algaja "
"režiimis ilmuvad harjutused üksteise järel, kui oled nad läbi teinud, "
"kogenud kirjutajad saavad aga kohe kasutada kõiki harjutusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Think about your choice, you won't able to change the type of a profile "
"later. But you can always create new profiles to revisit this decision."
msgstr ""
"Mõtle hoolega valik läbi: profiili tüüpi ei saa hiljem muuta. Muidugi saab "
"alati luua uue profiili, milles langetada teistsugune valik."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Welcome screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch;i avaekraan</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Welcome screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch;i avaekraan</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After pressing <guibutton>Start Training</guibutton> you will be taken to "
"the home screen. This screen will also be the first screen visible when you "
"run &i18n-ktouch; the next time."
msgstr ""
"Pärast vajutamist nupule <guibutton>Alusta harjutamist</guibutton> ilmub "
"koduaken. See on ühtlasi avaaken &i18n-ktouch;i järgmisel käivitamisel"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Picking a lesson"
msgstr "Õppetunni valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The home screen of &i18n-ktouch; consists of a toolbar and the course "
"selector. For more information see <xref linkend=\"training_preparation\"/>."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch;i koduaken koosneb tööriistaribast ja kursusevalijast. "
"Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <xref linkend=\"training_preparation\"/>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Home screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch;i koduaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Home screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch;i koduaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will show you the first course available for your current "
"keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; näitab esimest antud klaviatuuripaigutusele saadaolevat "
"kursust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch between courses or choose <link linkend=\"custom_lessons"
"\">custom lessons</link> by clicking their thumbnails in the right part of "
"the window."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some platforms, especially on &Microsoft; &Windows;, automatic keyboard "
"layout detection is not available. In that case you have to click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar, "
"select <guisubmenu> Configure Keyboard...</guisubmenu> submenu and choose "
"the name of keyboard layout or some keyboard layout which is similar to "
"yours. If your keyboard is not included, you can define your own keyboard "
"layout yourself, see <xref linkend=\"create_layouts\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Mõnel platvormil, eriti &Microsoft; &Windows;, ei ole klaviatuuripaigutuse "
"automaatne tuvastamine võimalik. Sellisel juhul tuleb tööriistaribal "
"klõpsata nupule <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, valida "
"alammenüü <guisubmenu>Klaviatuuri seadistamine...</guisubmenu> ja sealt enda "
"või sellele lähedane klaviatuuripaigutus. Kui sinu klaviatuuri loendis ei "
"leidu, võib ise paigutuse määrata, millest kõneleb lähemalt <xref linkend="
"\"create_layouts\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your lesson from the list on left of the window. You cannot choose "
"the locked lessons with <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> as they are too difficult for your current skills. Pass "
"lessons to unlock new ones. The preview of the selected lesson will be shown "
"on the right of lessons list."
msgstr ""
"Akna vasakpoolsest osast saab valida õppetunni. Valida ei saa lukustatud "
"õppetunde ikooniga <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, seest need on su määratud oskusi arvestades liiga "
"rasked. Uute õppetundideni jõudmiseks läbi varasemad. Paremal, õppetundide "
"loendis, näeb valitud õppetunni eelvaatlust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More information about the selected course can be shown and hidden again "
"using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button next to the course title."
msgstr ""
"Rohkem teavet õppetunni kohta saab näha ja uuesti varjata kursuse nime "
"kõrval asuva nupuga <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-dialog-information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you finished with the selection click on <guibutton>Start Training</"
"guibutton> to go to the training &i18n-ktouch; screen."
msgstr ""
"Kui valik on tehtud, klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Alusta harjutamist</"
"guibutton>, mis avab &i18n-ktouch;i harjutamisakna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training"
msgstr "Harjutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "The training window of &i18n-ktouch; shows three main sections:"
msgstr "&i18n-ktouch;i harjutamisaken koosneb kolmest põhiosast:"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some typing statistics in info boxes at the top"
msgstr "Teatud statistika kirjutamise kohta ülaosas"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text you need to type"
msgstr "Tekst, mida pead kirjutama"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "The keyboard visualization"
msgstr "Klaviatuuri kujutis"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The training screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch;i harjutamisaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The training screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch;i harjutamisaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Visibility of training screen parts can be configured using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Harjutamisaknas näha olevaid osasid saab seadistada <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch;i seadistustedialoogis</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place your two index fingers on the two keys on your keyboard with the two "
"little tactile markers near the center of the middle character row. With "
"that done your other fingers will find their intended keys almost "
"automatically. Your thumbs should rest above the space key, the only key you "
"will ever use them for when touch typing. The other fingers should be placed "
"on the three keys adjacent to the marked keys on the center row. Keys for "
"the same finger are grouped together through their color. Try to move your "
"hands as little as possible and always try to return your fingers to their "
"resting positions after you have typed a character."
msgstr ""
"Aseta mõlemad nimetissõrmed klaviatuuri kahele klahvile, mis on kujutisel "
"tähistatud keskmises reas kahe esiletõstmisega. Ülejäänud sõrmed peaksid "
"enam-vähem iseenesest leidma õige koha. Pöidlad peavad viibima tühikuklahvi "
"kohal, mis on ka ainuke klahv, mille jaoks pöidlaid kirjutamise ajal "
"kasutada. Ülejäänud kolm sõrme peavad paiknema samas reas kõrval asuvate "
"klahvide kohal. Klahvid, mida tuleb vajutada ühe ja sama sõrmega, on värvide "
"kaupa rühmitatud. Ürita liigutada käsi võimalikult vähe ning kui oled tähe "
"kirjutanud, too sõrm alati vaikimisi asukohta tagasi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start typing the text in the middle of the screen. The next key you have to "
"press is always highlighted on the keyboard visualization. While you type "
"you may make mistakes and hit the wrong key. In that case the characters "
"will displayed in red and you have to hit &Backspace; as often as necessary "
"to erase the wrongly typed characters."
msgstr ""
"Hakka kirjutama akna keskosas asuvat teksti. Klahv, mida tuleb vajutada, on "
"klaviatuuri kujutisel alati esile tõstetud. On täiesti usutav, et teed "
"kirjutamise ajal ka mõne vea. Sel juhul muudavad tähed värvi (vaikimisi "
"punaseks) ning sa pead vajuta klahvi &Backspace;, et vigane täht või tähed "
"kustutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
#| "<keycap>Return</keycap> to advance to the next line."
msgid ""
"When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
"&Enter; to advance to the next line."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled rea edukalt kirja pannud, vajuta klahvi <keycap>Return</keycap> "
"uuele reale liikumiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The key used to advance to the next line can be changed using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>"
msgstr ""
"Järgmisele reale liikumise klahvi saab muuta <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch;i seadistustedialoogis</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Review your progress"
msgstr "Edenemise jälgimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have completed a lesson &i18n-ktouch; will switch to the score "
"screen. It displays your current training and lesson statistics and shows a "
"graphical history of previous training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled õppetunni läbinud, avab &i18n-ktouch; statistikadialoogi. See "
"näitab sinu parajasti käsiloleva harjutuse ja õppetunni statistikat ning "
"graafiliselt varasemate harjutusseansside statistikat."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Statistics dialog of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch;i statistikadialoog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Statistics dialog of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch;i statistikadialoog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the statistics dialog you can select to show a particular lesson or "
"<guilabel>All Lessons</guilabel>. This is useful to distinguish between "
"overall performance and skill in certain lessons."
msgstr ""
"Statistikadialoogis saab lasta näidata nii konkreetset õppetundi kui ka "
"<guilabel>kõiki õppetunde</guilabel>. Nii saab vahet teha üldisel edenemisel "
"ja konkreetsetes õppetundides omandatud oskustel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you feel ready for the next lesson press <guibutton>Next lesson</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar to continue with the next lesson of the "
"current course or <guibutton>Repeat lesson</guibutton> button to try your "
"skills on the current lesson again. The <guibutton>Next lesson</guibutton> "
"button will be only available if you have passed the lesson."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled valmis järgmiseks õppetunniks, klõpsa tööriistaribal nupule "
"<guibutton>Järgmine õppetund</guibutton>, mis viib aktiivse kursuse järgmise "
"õppetunni juurde, või nupule <guibutton>Korda õppetundi</guibutton>, mis "
"võimaldab parandada oskusi läbitud õppetunnis. Nuppu <guibutton>Järgmine "
"õppetund</guibutton> saab kasutada ainult siis, kui oled senise õppetunni "
"läbinud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to switch to some other lesson or course press <guibutton>Return "
"to Home Screen</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid lülituda mõnele teisele õppetunnile või kursusele, klõpsa nupule "
"<guibutton>Tagasi koduaknasse</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want to continue the training with &i18n-ktouch; just close "
"the application window."
msgstr ""
"Kui sa ei soovi enam &i18n-ktouch;iga kirjutamist harjutada, sulge lihtsalt "
"rakenduse aken."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training Preparation"
msgstr "Harjutamise ettevalmistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pretty much everything in the &i18n-ktouch; home screen should be self-"
"explanatory. The top toolbar is meant to be the place where you can view and "
"configure &i18n-ktouch; settings. The course selector can be used to view "
"the information about the courses and switch between them."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch;i koduaknas peaks üldiselt kõik olema selge ega vaja lähemat "
"kirjeldamist. Ülal asuv tööriistariba on mõeldud &i18n-ktouch;i seadistuste "
"vaatamiseks ja seadistamiseks. Kursusevalijaga saab näha teavet kursuste "
"kohta ja nende vahel lülituda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
