msgstr "&i18n-ktouch;i tööriistariba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar of &i18n-ktouch; houses the profile button at the left and the "
"application menu button at the right."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch;i tööriistaribal asub vasakul profiilinupp ja paremal "
"rakendusemenüü nupp."

