msgstr ""
"Võimalik on uurida olemasolevate profiilide seadistusi, neid kustutada või "
"luua uue profiili nupuga <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To switch to the review mode press <guibutton>Edit</guibutton>. To select a "
"profile and return to the home screen press <guibutton>Use Selected Profile "
"</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
