msgstr ""
"Nupuga <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guilabel>Tavaline klahv</guilabel> saab lisada paigutusele uue tavalise "
"klahvi, nupuga <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guilabel>Eriklahv</guilabel> uue eriklahvi (muuteklahv, "
"<keycap>tühikuklahv</keycap>, &Backspace;, &Tab;, <keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> "
"või &Enter;). Nupuga <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Kustuta</guilabel> saab valitud klahvi "
"paigutusest eemaldada. Skaleerimist saab muuta liuguriga redaktori "
"tööriistariba vasakpoolses osas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The properties of individual keys can be edited using the bottom pane of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Konkreetsete klahvide omadusi saab muuta redaktoriakna alumist paneeli "
"kasutades."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal keys"
msgstr "Tavalised klahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is easy to change the size or properties of a key."
msgstr "Klahvi suurust või omadusi on hõlpus muuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Begin by clicking on the key you want to change. This selects the clicked "
"key as the current key."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa kõigepealt klahvile, mida tahad muuta. See valib klõpsatud klahvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are now 4 squares on the corners of the key. By dragging these "
"squares, you will be able to drag the key border to a new location. Dragging "
"the whole key allows you to change the key position in the layout."
msgstr ""
"Klahvi nurkadesse tekib nüüd neli ruudukest. Neid lohistades saab "
"klahvipiirde viia uude asendisse. Kogu klahvi lohistamine võimaldab muuta "
"selle klahvi asetust klaviatuuripaigutuses."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numerical characteristics of the key geometry can also be changed using "
"the <guilabel>Geometry</guilabel> section of the pane at the bottom of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Muuta saab ka klahvi geomeetria arvväärtusi, kasutades selleks redaktoriakna "
"allosas asuva paneeli sektsiooni <guilabel>Geomeetria</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Editing an individual key properties</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Klahvi omaduste muutmine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Editing an individual key properties</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Klahvi omaduste muutmine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom pane can also be used to choose finger to press the key and "
"switch the haptic marker for the key."
msgstr ""
"All paikneval paneelil saab samuti valida sõrme, millega klahvi tuleb "
"vajutada, ja vajaduse korral lisada klahvile puutemarker (mis reaalsel "
"klahvil avaldub väikese kriipsukujulise kõrgendina)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key characters"
msgstr "Klahvi tähed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The characters that will be shown on a key can be changed using the "
"<guilabel> Characters</guilabel> section of the editor bottom pane."
msgstr ""
"Tähti, mida klahvil näidatakse, saab muuta redaktori allosas asuva paneeli "
"sektsioonis <guilabel>Märgid</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Editing the character position</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Märgi asukoha muutmine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1362
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Editing the character position</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Märgi asukoha muutmine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a character by pressing <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button. A selected character can be removed by pressing "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button."
msgstr ""
"Märgi saab lisada nupule <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> klõpsates. Valitud märgi saab eemaldada nupule "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> klõpsates."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select the position of individual characters on the key by "
"double-clicking in the <guilabel>Position</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"Samuti saab valida konkreetse märgi asukoha klahvil, kui teha topeltklõps "
"veerus <guilabel>Asukoht</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifiers"
msgstr "Muuteklahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several modifier keys that can be defined in &i18n-ktouch;. They "
"can be edited as normal keys but it is helpful to know identifier of "
"modifier key to use them as appropriate. The table of modifier keys "
"identifiers is given below."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; võimaldab määrata mitmeid muuteklahve. Neid saab muuta nagu "
"tavalisi klahve, kuid sobivaks kasutamiseks on mõistlik teada muuteklahvi "
"identifikaatorit. Muuteklahvide identifikaatorid on ära toodud allolevas "
"tabelis."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier keys"
msgstr "Muuteklahvid"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier key"
msgstr "Muuteklahv"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier id in &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "Muuteklahvi ID &i18n-ktouch;is"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Alt;"
msgstr "&Alt;"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid "altgr"
msgstr "altgr"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;"
msgstr "&Shift;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1403
#, no-c-format
