msgstr "<literal>left_shift</literal> või <literal>right_shift</literal>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Lessons"
msgstr "Kohandatud õppetunnid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom lessons feature allows you to extend your training material in an "
"easy way by choosing some arbitrary text."
msgstr ""
"Kohandatud õppetundide võimalus lubab hõlpsasti laiendada harjutusmaterjali "
"suvalist teksti valides."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom lessons are gathered in a special course, the <guilabel>Custom "
"Lessons</guilabel> course, always available right next to <link linkend="
"\"picking_a_lesson\">the normal built-in courses</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kohandatud õppetunnid koondatakse eriliseks kursuseks nimega "
"<guilabel>Kohandatud õppetunnid</guilabel>, mis on alati näha paremal pool "
"<link linkend=\"picking_a_lesson\">tavalistest kaasa pandud kursustest</"
"link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom lessons course</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kohandatud õppetundide kursus</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Custom lessons course</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kohandatud õppetundide kursus</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1434
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This special course mostly acts like any other, training and statistics "
#| "gathering works as usual. Clicking on <guibutton>Create New Custom "
#| "Lesson</guibutton> or the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button (for "
#| "existing lessons) brings up a stripped-down version of <link linkend="
#| "\"adding_lessons\">the normal lesson editor</link>."
msgid ""
"This special course mostly acts like any other, training and statistics "
"gathering works as usual. Clicking on <guibutton>Add New Lesson</guibutton> "
"or the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button (the pencil icon for existing "
"lessons) brings up a stripped-down version of <link linkend=\"adding_lessons"
"\">the normal lesson editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"See erikursus on üldjoontest sarnane teistega. Samamoodi käib nii "
"harjutamine kui ka statistika kogumine. Klõps nupule <guibutton>Loo uus "
"kohandatud õppetund</guibutton> või <guibutton>Muuda</guibutton> "
"(olemasolevate õppetundide korral) avab <link linkend=\"adding_lessons"
"\">tavalise õppetundide redaktori</link> kärbitud versiooni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom lesson editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kohandatud õppetunni redaktor</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Custom lesson editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kohandatud õppetunni redaktor</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1452
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The editor will highlight problematic sections of your lesson texts. "
#| "Characters which can't by typed on your keyboard layout will be shown on "
#| "a dark red, lines which are considered to be too long use a gray font for "
#| "the excess characters."
msgid ""
"The editor will highlight problematic sections of your lesson texts. "
"Characters which can't by typed on your keyboard layout will be shown on a "
"dark red background, lines which are considered to be too long use a pink "
"background for the excess characters. &i18n-ktouch; requires that every line "
"of the lesson does not exceed the recommended 60 characters limit."
msgstr ""
"Redaktor tõstab esile õppetunni tekstide problemaatilised osad. Märke, mida "
"ei saa kirjutada sinu klaviatuuripaigutusega, näidatakse tumepunaselt. "
"Ridade puhul, mida peetakse liiga pikaks, näidatakse üleliigseid märke "
"hallilt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Done</guibutton> button to confirm your edits or close "
"the editor window to cancel them."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All custom lessons are stored per profile and keyboard layout individually. "
"Use this to manage different sets of lessons depending on the specific "
"training situation."
msgstr ""
"Kõik kohandatud õppetunnid salvestatakse eraldi vastavalt profiilile ja "
"klaviatuuripaigutusele. Nii saab vastavalt konkreetsele harjutamisolukorrale "
"kasutada erinevaid õppetunnikomplekte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sharing your results"
msgstr "Tulemuste jagamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to save your courses and keyboard layouts in separate files "
"outside of the local &i18n-ktouch; database."
msgstr ""
"Oma kursused ja klaviatuuripaigutused võib salvestada ka eraldi failidesse "
"väljaspool kohalikku &i18n-ktouch;i andmebaasi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export/Import"
msgstr "Eksport ja import"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export a course or keyboard layout in a separate file choose the "
"corresponding item in the list at the left part of <guilabel>Course and "
"Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window and press <guibutton>Export</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Kursuse või klaviatuuripaigutuse eksportimiseks eraldi faili vali vajalik "
"kirje <guilabel>kursuse ja klaviatuuritüübi redaktori</guilabel> akna "
"vasakpoolses servas ja klõpsa tööriistaribal nupule <guibutton>Ekspordi</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open a standard &kde; save dialog. Description of this "
"dialog in details can be found in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/files."
"html\">Opening and Saving Files</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; avab standardse &kde; salvestamisdialoogi. Selle kirjelduse "
"leiab &kde; põhialuste käsiraamatu peatükist <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"files.html\">Failide avamine ja salvestamine</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the name and the location of the &XML; file to be saved."
msgstr "Valida saab salvestatava &XML;-faili nime ja asukoha."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find it worth to share your files with over users, please send them "
"with some description to <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-edu@kde.org\">kde-edu "
"mailing list</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Kui arvad, et sinu failid võiksid huvi pakkuda ka teistele, saada palun need "
"postiloendisse <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-edu@kde.org\">kde-edu mailing list</"
"ulink>, lisades lühikese kirjelduse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Your data should be licensed under <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/"
#| "licenses/gpl-2.0.html\">GNU General Public License, version 2</ulink> to "
#| "include them into the default &i18n-ktouch; installation."
msgid ""
"Your data should be licensed under <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/"
"gpl-2.0.html\">&GNU; General Public License, version 2</ulink> to include "
"them into the default &i18n-ktouch; installation."
msgstr ""
"Et kaasa panna &i18n-ktouch;i vaikimisi paigaldusega, peavad sinu andmed "
"olema litsentsitud vastavalt <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/"
"gpl-2.0.html\">GNU Üldise Avaliku Litsentsi versioonile 2</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To import your data files into &i18n-ktouch; press <guibutton>Import</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar and choose &XML; file that was earlier "
"exported using &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"Oma andmefaili importimiseks &i18n-ktouch;i klõpsa tööriistaribal nupule "
"<guibutton>Impordi</guibutton> ja vali &XML;-fail, mis oli varem eksporditud "
"&i18n-ktouch;i vahendusel."

